Package com.portfolio.restapi.entities

Class Trade

java.lang.Object
com.portfolio.restapi.entities.Trade
@Entity public class Trade extends Object
Represents a trade entity for a financial application. Each Trade object encapsulates information about a trade transaction, including stock details, volume, buy or sell action, and status code.
